{
  "page": "Gorys Edoryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\"><img alt=\"Volantis.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/50px-Volantis.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/75px-Volantis.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/100px-Volantis.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Paymaster</span><br />Gorys Edoryen</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Gorys_Edoryen_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gorys Edoryen TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/Gorys_Edoryen_TheMico.jpg/350px-Gorys_Edoryen_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/Gorys_Edoryen_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Gorys Edoryen, by TheMico ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nPaymaster</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gorys Edoryen</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Paymaster\" title=\"Paymaster\">paymaster</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Gorys_Edoryen\" title=\"Category:Images of Gorys Edoryen\">Images of Gorys Edoryen</a></div>\n<p>Gorys is as pale and thin as a cadaver. He has a pointed black beard, but blood-red hair that tumbles about his shoulders in oiled ringlets. He wears a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>'s ransom in <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">golden</a> arm rings, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Leopard\" title=\"Leopard\">leopard</a> skin draped across one shoulder.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Gorys is originally from <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>. He replaced Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a> as the Golden Company's paymaster after Strickland's promotion to <a href=\"/index.php/Captain-general\" title=\"Captain-general\">captain-general</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Gorys Edoryen is present during <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>'s rendezvous with the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> three miles south of <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a>. When <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> reveals that \"Young Griff\" is, in fact, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a>, silence greets his announcement. He notices Gorys playing with one of his corkscrew curls and murmuring something in a tongue he does not know.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When discussing <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, Edoryen urges feigning acceptance of the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkish</a> envoy’s offer of a contract to fight against Daenerys. However, <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a> replies that one broken contract is stain enough upon the honor of the company.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Edoryen, like the rest of the company, swears his allegiance to Aegon before they <a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">invade Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Taking of Griffin&#39;s Roost\">takes Griffin's Roost</a> with some men of the company. The rest of the men remain in camp to guard their landing site and the prince, under the command of Gorys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_scenes\">Behind the scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In an early draft of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, Edoryen is the <a href=\"/index.php/Captain-general\" title=\"Captain-general\">captain-general</a> of the Golden Company, not the paymaster.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gorys_Edoryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, The Lost Lord.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 61\">Chapter 61</a>, The Griffin Reborn.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/asoiaf/comments/10cq27q/spoilers_extended_secrets_of_the_cushing_library/\">https://www.reddit.com/r/asoiaf/comments/10cq27q/spoilers_extended_secrets_of_the_cushing_library/</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Paymaster\" title=\"Paymaster\">Paymaster</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_296_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">296&#160;AC</a>–present        <br /><small>Served under: <b><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a></b></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Incumbent</b>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404093808\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.102 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.311 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1412/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 13408/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8587/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1077/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2553/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.59 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n